metadata.name: France is... Abstract
metadata.description:
Francis Bacon is the subject, but not as you know him. This is because of reading about a misinterpretation of a famous quote. "Knowledge is power - France is Bacon." That got me thinking. What else could France be?

This is a bundled purchase. In addition to the NFT, the primary winning collector will also receive the original signed painting on paper (50 x 50cm).

**Contact me via Twitter or the contact form on my site (leeellis.art) to arrange delivery once purchased. You will have 4 weeks to claim the painting.
